rComments: Slides look like textbooks. Lectures are really long and boring and he makes it hard to tell what's important material or not. Labs are fine

BIO 4558 is a great class. R is used a LOT in the class but the prof explains it really well in his R Manual. The marking could be pretty specific, make sure to answer the questions specifically. 8 lab reports, no final exam or midterms, just a data analysis project.
